%% PATIENT_MANAGEMENT Processing Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant MainLoop
    participant HABADTE

    MainLoop->>HABADTE: load transfer record
    HABADTE-->>MainLoop: record loaded

    MainLoop->>HABADTE: BR 017 file indicator zero
    HABADTE-->>MainLoop: skip or continue

    MainLoop->>HABADTE: BR 018 flag void
    HABADTE-->>MainLoop: skip or continue

    MainLoop->>HABADTE: BR 019 io flag outpatient
    HABADTE-->>MainLoop: skip or include
